member.remarks:
You have item with a icon from build-in preset:
    ribbonButton1.IconSet.Add(new C1.Framework.C1BitmapIcon("Book", new System.Drawing.Size(32, 32), System.Drawing.Color.Transparent, "Preset_LargeImages", 22));
You can get this image:
    var bookImage = c1ribbon.GetPressetImage(ribbonButton1.IconSet[1].Key, 32);
The C1Ribbon contains 16px, 20px and 32px build-in presets.

